w-the-bond-market-could-trigger-the-next-financial-crisis-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egovernment%20debt%3C%2Fa%3E.%20It%20means%20Trump%20will%20be%20forced%20to%20lower%20the%20bar%20on%20his%20promises%20to%20avoid%20shaving%20too%20much%20off%20government%20revenue.%20Otherwise%2C%20the%20budget%20and%20deficit%20would%20explode%2C%20Barraud%20noted.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20example%2C%20if%20Trump%20wants%20to%20make%20the%20Tax%20Cuts%20and%20Jobs%20Act%20of%202017%20permanent%2C%20the%20promised%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Fstock-market-outlook-trump-tax-cuts-sp500-prediction-earnings-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecorporate%20tax-rate%3C%2Fa%3E%20cut%20of%2015%25%20may%20need%20to%20look%20more%20like%2017%25%20or%2018%25%2C%20he%20noted.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBased%20on%20information%20pulled%20from%20the%20Congressional%20Budget%20Office%2C%20the%20Tax%20Foundation%2C%20and%20conversations%20Barraud%20is%20having%20with%20clients%2C%20including%20large%20banks%20and%20hedge%20funds%2C%20he%20has%20concluded%20that%20if%20the%20deficit%20exceeds%20the%20threshold%20of%207.5%25%20to%208%25%20of%20GDP%20annually%2C%20it%20would%20significantly%20impact%20long-duration%20US%20Treasuries.%20The%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Fmarkets%2Fus%2Fus-budget-deficit-tops-18-trillion-fiscal-2024-third-largest-record-2024-10-18%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20fiscal%20budget%20gap%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%202024%20is%206.4%25%2C%20up%20from%202023's%20deficit%20of%206.2%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20idea%20is%20that%20if%20the%20deficit%20is%20above%20this%20threshold%2C%20the%20interest%20rate%20on%20the%2010-year%20could%20go%20beyond%205%25%2C%20and%20it'll%20have%20a%20negative%20effect%20on%20the%20economy%2C%20especially%20for%20the%20housing%20market%2C%26quot%3B%20Barraud%20said.%20%26quot%3BSo%20we%20think%20that%20beyond%205%25%2C%20there%20could%20be%20negative%20spillover%2C%20and%20that%20could%20be%20counterproductive.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20spillover%20would%20go%20beyond%20mortgage%20rates.%20As%20the%20yield%20rises%2C%20servicing%20US%20debt%20would%20become%20more%20expensive%2C%20borrowing%20costs%20for%20companies%20and%20consumers%20would%20rise%2C%20and%20at%20some%20point%2C%20multiples%20would%20come%20under%20pressure%2C%20hurting%20the%20stock%20market%2C%20too%2C%20he%20noted.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFinally%2C%20inflation%20could%20be%20higher%20than%20expected%20in%202025.%20He%20projects%20the%20consumer%20price%20index%20averaging%202.5%25.%20A%20stronger%20labor%20market%20will%20cause%20this%2C%20especially%20wage%20growth%20and%20new%20job%20creation%2C%20combined%20with%20labor%20shortages%20from%20restrictive%20immigration%20policy.%20And%20as%20tariffs%20take%20effect%20toward%20the%20end%20of%20the%20year%2C%20it%20could%20further%20boost%20inflation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2F2025-forecasts-projections-inflation-gdp-deficit-most-accurate-economist-barraud-2024-11%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1732357921000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6740bb969f2901eb603662d0%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2F2025-forecasts-projections-inflation-gdp-deficit-most-accurate-economist-barraud-2024-11%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22His%20economic%20models%20forecast%20with%20precision%20and%20startling%20accuracy.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22lmaidan%40businessinsider.com%20(Laila%20Maidan)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A101%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2F2025-forecasts-projections-inflation-gdp-deficit-most-accurate-economist-barraud-2024-11%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22A%20historian%20says%20the%20naval%20battle%20in%20'Gladiator%20II'%20only%20got