arrested%20on%20the%20ICC%20arrest%20warrant%20if%20he%20travelled%20to%20the%20UK.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrime%20Minister%20Keir%20Starmer's%20spokesman%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BThe%20UK%20will%20always%20comply%20with%20its%20legal%20obligations%20as%20set%20out%20by%20domestic%20law%20and%20indeed%20international%20law.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20he%20refused%20to%20be%20drawn%20specifically%20on%20whether%20UK%20police%20would%20detain%20Netanyahu%2C%20telling%20reporters%20he%20would%20not%20%26quot%3Bget%20into%20hypotheticals%20in%20relation%20to%20individual%20cases%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBoth%20the%20UK%20and%20Canada%20are%20part%20of%20the%20Five%20Eyes%2C%20an%20intelligence%20alliance%20also%20composed%20of%20Australia%2C%20New%20Zealand%2C%20and%20the%20United%20States.%20Other%20countries%20that%20agreed%20to%20follow%20through%20with%20the%20ICC's%20decision%20include--%20Belgium%2C%20the%20European%20Union%2C%20France%2C%20Iran%2C%20Ireland%2C%20Jordan%2C%20The%20Netherlands%2C%20Norway%2C%20Sweden%2C%20South%20Africa%2C%20Switzerland%2C%20and%20Turkey%20among%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOther%20key%20Five%20Eyes%20member%20US%20has%2C%20however%2C%20called%20the%20move%20'outrageous'.%20%26quot%3BThe%20ICC%20issuance%20of%20arrest%20warrants%20against%20Israeli%20leaders%20is%20outrageous%2C%26quot%3B%20President%20Joe%20Biden%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLet%20me%20be%20clear%20once%20again%3A%20whatever%20the%20ICC%20might%20imply%2C%20there%20is%20no%20equivalence%20-%20none%20-%20between%20Israel%20and%20Hamas.%20We%20will%20always%20stand%20with%20Israel%20against%20threats%20to%20its%20security%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20statement%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20warrant%20was%20supported%20by%C2%A0US%20Senator%20Bernie%20Sanders%2C%20who%20took%20to%20X%20and%20said%3A%20%E2%80%9CAll%20launched%20indiscriminate%20attacks%20against%20civilians%20and%20caused%20unimaginable%20hu