ll%20chunk%20-%20around%2014%20-%20comes%20from%20seats%20are%20those%20contested%20by%20other%20parties%2C%20mostly%20the%20BJP%20or%20Congress%2C%20in%202019%20and%20given%20to%20the%20Shinde%20Sena%20and%20Ajit%20Pawar%20this%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20rest%20have%20been%20flipped%20from%20their%20parent%20parties%2C%20and%20this%2C%20potentially%2C%20is%20one%20of%20the%20areas%20where%20the%20Maha%20Vikas%20Aghadi%20lost%20this%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Shinde%20Sena%20and%20Ajit%20Pawar's%20NCP%20contested%2081%20and%2059%20seats%20in%20this%20election%2C%20and%20they%20are%20leading%20in%2055%20and%2040%20seats%2C%20respectively.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20other%20side%2C%20Thackeray's%20Sena%20contested%2095%20seats%20but%20is%20leading%20only%20in%2020%2C%20and%20Sharad%20Pawar's%20NCP%20contested%2086%20seats%20but%20is%20leading%20only%20in%2011.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOf%20the%20Shinde%20Sena's%2057%20leads%2C%20at%20least%2040%20are%20seats%20won%20by%20the%20undivided%20Sena%20in%20the%202019%20election.%20Similarly%2C%20of%20Ajit%20Pawar's%20NCP's%2037%20leads%2C%20a%20staggering%2032%20were%20won%20by%20Sharad%20Pawar's%20NCP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHad%20the%20Sena%20and%20NCP%20not%20split%2C%20it%20would%20have%20handed%20the%20MVA%20those%2070-odd%20seats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20would%20not%2C%20perhaps%2C%20have%20been%20enough%20for%20the%20Maha%20Vikas%20Aghadi%20to%20win%20this%20election%2C%20but%20it%20would%20certainly%20have%20been%20enough%20to%20push%20the%20BJP%20to%20a%20much%20closer%20finish.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20Exit%20Polls%20Said%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20MVA%20had%20only%20been%20given%20a%20(very)%20slim%20chance%20of%20upsetting%20the%20in-power%20BJP-led%20alliance's%20applecart%20in%20the%20final%20election%20of%20the%20year%3B%20only%20one%20of%2011%20exit%20polls%20studied%20by%20NDTV%20believed%20it%20can%20win.%20Three%20others%20were%20on%20the%20fence%20but%20even%20they%20tilted%20to%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi's%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20average%20of%20those%2011%20exit%20polls%20gives%20the%20Mahayuti%20155%20seats%20and%20the%20MVA%20only%20120%2C%20with%20smaller%20parties%20and%20independent%20candidates%20expected%20to%20get%20the%20remaining%2013.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20a%20health%20warning%3A%20exit%20polls%20often%20get%20it%20wrong.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20majority%20of%20those%20exit%20polls%20predicted%20a%20big%20win%20for%20the%20Mahayuti.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmaharashtra-assembly-election-result-exit-polls-predict-mahayuti-win-mahayuti-vs-maha-vikas-on-fraud-exit-polls-as-maharashtra-awaits-election-result-7070910%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMahayuti%20vs%20MVA%20On%20%26quot%3BFraud%26quot%3B%20Exit%20Polls%20As%20Maharashtra%20Awaits%20Result%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAcross%20the%20aisle%2C%20only%20one%20-%20Electoral%20Edge%20-%20expected%20the%20Congress'%20alliance%20to%20win%20and%2C%20even%20then%2C%20by%20five%20seats%20only%2C%20with%2020%20seats%20from%20smaller%20parties%20and%20independents%20in%20play%20for%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20Happened%20In%202019%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%202019%20election%20resulted%20in%20a%20thumping%20win%20for%20the%20BJP%20and%20the%20undivided%20Sena%3B%20the%20saffron%20party%20won%20105%20seats%20(down%2017%20from%202014)%20and%20its%20ally%2056%20(down%20seven).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20two%20long-time%20allies%20fell%20out%2C%20quite%20spectacularly%2C%20in%20the%20following%20days%20after%20they%20failed%20to%20agree%20a%20power-sharing%20deal.%20Mr%20Thackeray%20then%20led%20his%20Sena%20into%20a%20surprise%20alliance%20with%20the%20Congress%20and%20Sharad%20Pawar's%20NCP%20(then%20also%20undivided)%20to%20shut%20out%20a%20furious%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMuch%20to%20t