which%20is%20lagging%20far%20behind%20at%2056.%20The%20BJP%20leads%20the%20Mahayuti%20show%2C%20leading%20in%20124%20out%20of%20the%20148%20seats%20it%20contested.%20It%20has%20been%20supported%20well%20by%20its%20allies%20--%20Eknath%20Shinde's%20Shiv%20Sena%20and%20Ajit%20Pawar's%20NCP.%20Both%20have%20surged%20ahead%20of%20their%20rival%20factions%20led%20by%20Uddhav%20Thackeray%20and%20Sharad%20Pawar%20in%20an%20election%20seen%20as%20a%20fight%20to%20prove%20which%20faction%20is%20the%20'real%20Sena'%20and%20the%20'real%20NCP'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20Mahayuti%20camp%20has%20much%20to%20celebrate%20today%2C%20complications%20are%20waiting%20in%20the%20wings.%20And%20these%20complications%20are%20similar%20to%20the%20ones%20that%20emerged%20after%20the%202019%20Maharashtra%20election%2C%20also%20won%20by%20NDA.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWho%20Will%20Be%20Chief%20Minister%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20big%20question%20that%20emerges%20after%20the%20NDA's%20victory%20is%20--%20who%20will%20be%20the%20next%20Maharashtra%20Chief%20Minister%3F%20Both%20Mr%20Fadnavis%20and%20Mr%20Shinde%20are%20cruising%20to%20comfortable%20victories%20in%20Nagpur%20South-West%20and%20Kopdi%20Pachpakhadi%20seats%2C%20respectively.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20is%20the%20anchor%20of%20the%20Mahayuti%20alliance%20and%20has%20scored%20the%20best%20strike%20rate%20among%20all%20NDA%20allies.%20Against%20this%20backdrop%2C%20the%20party%20is%20likely%20to%20push%20for%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20post%2C%20with%20senior%20leader%20Devendra%20Fadnavis%20as%20its%20clear%20choice.%20But%20the%20Shinde%20Sena%20may%20dig%20in%20its%20heels%20and%20argue%20that%20the%20Mahayuti%20went%20into%20the%20election%20with%20Eknath%20Shinde%20as%20the%20government's%20face%20and%20that%20the%20state%20government's%20policies%20and%20promises%20played%20a%20key%20role%20behind%20the%20massive%20mandate%20in%20this%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20when%20the%20rebellion%20led%20by%20Mr%20Shinde%20toppled%20the%20Uddhav%20Thackeray%20government%20and%20split%20Shiv%20Sena%2C%20the%20BJP%20had%20taken%20a%20moral%20high%20ground%20by%20giving%20up%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20post.%20But%20with%20over%20120%20MLAs%20in%20their%20kitty%2C%20they%20might%20not%20be%20so%20generous%20this%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlso%2C%20with%20all%20three%20allies%20performing%20in%20their%20strongholds%2C%20this%20verdict%20creates%20a%20breeding%20ground%20for%20hard%20bargains%20over%20ministerial%20posts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%202019%20Repeat%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInterestingly%2C%20the%20Maharashtra%20result%20may%20just%20create%20a%20situation%20similar%20to%20the%20post-poll%20scenario%20five%20years%20back.%20In%20the%202019%20state%20polls%2C%20the%20BJP%20had%20won%20105%20seats%20and%20the%20undivided%20Shiv%20Sena%2056.%20After%20the%20results%2C%20differences%20cropped%20up%20over%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20post.%20While%20Uddhav%20Thackeray%20claimed%20an%20understanding%20over%20rotational%20Chief%20Ministership%2C%20the%20BJP%20denied%20any%20such%20pact.%20Eventually%2C%20the%20Sena%20pulled%20the%20plug%2C%20ending%20one%20of%20the%20most%20enduring%20alliances%20in%20the%20BJP's%20history.%20Five%20years%20later%2C%20there%20are%20many%20more%20players%20in%20Maharashtra's%20political%20landscape%2C%20with%20two%20factions%20each%20of%20Sena%20and%20NCP%20fighting%20an%20identity%20battle.%20And%20this%20time%2C%20the%20way%20numbers%20stand%2C%20the%20BJP%20and%20Eknath%20Shinde%20are%20where%20the%20BJP%20and%20Uddhav%20Thackeray%20were%20five%20years%20back.%20The%20question%20then%20is%2C%20will%20Mr%20Shinde%20blink%20or%20this%20victory%20will%20create%20a%20bigger%20challenge%20for%20the%20BJP%3F%20Giving%20up%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20post%20may%20be%20seen%20as%20a%20stepdown%20and%20pushing%20for%20it%20risks%20a%20rift%20in%20the%20alliance.%20There%20is%2C%20however%2C%20a%20big%20difference%20vis-a-vis%202019.%20With%20Ajit%20Pawar's%20NCP%20putting%20up%20a%20good%20show%2C%20the%20BJP%20needs%20only%20one%20out%20of%20its%20two%20allies%20to%20reach%20the%20magic%20figure.%20The%20Shinde%20Sena%20will%20keep%20this%20in%20mind%20as%20it%20pushes%20for%20any%20bargain.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20the%20media%20as%20the%20trends%20showed%20a%20clear%20NDA%20edge%2C%20Mr%20Shinde%20had%20a%20cautious%20reply%20to%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20question.%20%26quot%3BWe%20will%20sit%20and%20decide%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20adding%2C%20%26quot%3B(Prime%20Minister%20Narendra)%20Modji%20is%20our%20senior.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Maha%20Vikas%20Aghadi%20Subplot%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20big%20story%20in%20this%20election%20is%20the%20stunning%20setback%20suffered%20by%20the%20Congress-led%20INDIA%20alliance%20that%20won%2030%20out%20of%2048%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%20in%20the%20general%20elections%20months%20back.%20The%20Maha%20Vikas%20Aghadi%20is%20now%20leading%20in%20just%2052%20seats%2C%20with%20the%20Congress%2C%20Shiv%20Sena%20(UBT)%20and%20NCP%20(Sharad%20Pawar)%20ahead%20in%2019%2C%2019%20and%2014%20seats%2C%20respectively.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERiding%20on%20its%20stellar%20show%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%2C%20the%20Congress%20had%20bargained%20hard%20to%20get%20the%20best%20deal%20during%20seat-sharing.%20With%20the%20Opposition%20party%20failing%20to%20convert%20these%20contests%20into%20wins%2C%20the%20Congress%20will%20be%20at%20the%20receiving%20end%20of%20criticism%20and%20may%20be%20accused%20of%20the%20pulling%20the%20alliance%20down.%20Politically%2C%20it%20is%20a%20massive%20setback%20for%20Uddhav%20Thackeray%20and%20Sharad%20Pawar%20in%20the%20fight%20for%20their%20party's%20identity.%20The%20two%20leaders%2C%20who%20have%20been%20trying%20to%20recover%20after%20mutinies%20split%20their%20party%2C%20now%20face%20an%20identity%20crisis%20as%20the%20breakaway%20factions%20score%20much%20better%20than%20their%20camps.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1732351020000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-06%2F8lvb2kno_devendra-fadnavis-eknath-shinde-devendra-fadnavis-ani_625x300_13_June_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2F2024-maharashtra-election-results-eknath-shinde-devendra-fadnavis-eknath-shinde-now-where-uddhav-thackeray-was-in-19-with-a-big-difference-7085808%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Four%20hours%20into%20the%20counting%20of%20votes%20for%20Maharashtra%20Assembly%20polls%2C%20the%20BJP-led%20Mahayuti%20seems%20set%20for%20a%20landslide%20win%2C%20bouncing%20back%20emphatically%20from%20its%20setback%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%20this%20year%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2F2024-maharashtra-election-results-eknath-shinde-devendra-fadnavis-eknath-shinde-now-where-uddhav-thackeray-was-in-19-with-a-big-difference-7085808%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%226%20Months%20After%20Lok%20Sabha%20High%2C%20Sharad%20Pawar's%20NCP%20Hits%20All-Time%20Low%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20Indian%20politics'%20most%20resilient%20figures%2C%20Sharad%20Pawar%2C%20has%20hinted%20that%20he%20will%20quit%20active%20politics%20after%20his%20Rajya%20Sabha%20term%20ends%20in%202026.%20If%20the%2083-year-old%20goes%20ahead%20with%20the%20plan%2C%20his%20retirement%20will%20come%20after%20his%20last%20Maharashtra%20Assembly%20elections%20at%20the%20helm%20of%20his%20party%20proving%20to%20be%20one%20of%20the%20biggest%20blots%20in%20an%20otherwise%20stellar%20career.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20things%20stood%20at%202%20pm%20on%20Saturday%2C%20the%20Sharad%20Pawar%20faction%20of%20the%20NCP%20was%20ahead%20in%20only%2013%20of%20the%20state's%20288%20seats%20after%20contesting%2087%20-%20a%20strike%20rate%20of%2014.94%25%2C%20which%20is%20the%20veteran%20leader's%20worst%20ever.%20What%20will%20add%20to%20this%20ignominy%20is%20that%20the%20party%20had%20a%20strike%20rate%20of%2080%25%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%20just%20six%20months%20ago.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20Sharad%20Pawar%20and%20his%20NCP%2C%20the%20thing%20that%20will%20probably%20hurt%20even%20more%20is%20the%20fact%20that%20it%20is%2026%20seats%20behind%20the%20Ajit%20Pawar%20faction%20in%20what%20was%20seen%20as%20an%20existential%20battle%20for%20both%20parties.%20The%20first%20contest%20between%20the%20Pawars%20after%20Ajit%20Pawar%20split%20the%20party%20last%20year%20was%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%20and%20Sharad%20Pawar%20had%20achieved%20a%20decisive%20victory%20there%2C%20laying%20claim%20to%20his%20group%20being%20the%20real%20NCP%20despite%20the%20rival%20faction%20getting%20the%20original%20name%20and%20symbol.%20In%20the%20second%20-%20and%20arguably%20more%20important%20-%20bout%20in%20the%20Assembly%20elections%2C%20Ajit%20Pawar's%20group%20is%20set%20to%20emerge%20the%20victor%2C%20leading%20in%2039%20seats%20against%20the%20Sharad%20Pawar%20faction's%2013.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%202019%20Maharashtra%20Assembly%20polls%2C%20the%20undivided%20NCP%20had%20won%2054%20seats%2C%20more%20than%20its%20ally%20Congress%2C%20which%20managed%20to%20clinch%2044%2C%20but%20even%20that%20has%20changed%20in%20these%20elections.%20This%20year%2C%20Sharad%20Pawar's%20NCP%20is%20set%20to%20have%20the%20lowest%20number%20of%20Assembly%20seats%20among%20major%20political%20parties%20in%20the%20state%2C%20behind%20the%20Congress%20and%20even%20Uddhav%20Thackeray's%20Shiv%20Sena%2C%20whose%20party%20had%20also%20suffered%20a%20split%20following%20a%20rebellion%20by%20Eknath%20Shinde%20in%202022.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPolitical%20Chops%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESharad%20Pawar%20has%20been%20in%20politics%20for%20nearly%20six%20decades%2C%20and%20has%20served%20as%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20of%20Maharashtra%20four%20times%2C%20even%20be