0x800.jpeg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FVani-2-1732274640-150x100.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-382087%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22853%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EHealth%20emergencies%2C%20like%20Bruno%E2%80%99s%2C%20made%20Vivek%20and%20Vani%20realise%20the%20need%20for%20devices%20that%20could%20monitor%20a%20pet%E2%80%99s%20vitals.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CVivek%20and%20I%20have%20been%20pet%20parents%20for%20life.%20The%20limited%20insights%20into%20our%20pets%E2%80%99%20health%2C%20coupled%20with%20the%20sudden%20onset%20of%20health%20issues%2C%20prompted%20us%20to%20seek%20global%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F341951%2Fratan-tata-trust-small-animal-hospital-veterinary-dogs-cats-pets-mumbai-mahalaxmi%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esolutions%20for%20pet%20healthcare%3C%2Fa%3E.%20We%20came%20across%20wearables%20that%20functioned%20primarily%20as%20trackers.%20Driven%20by%20our%20personal%20needs%20for%20our%20own%20pets%2C%20we%20delved%20deeply%20into%20the%20animal%20healthcare%20sector%2C%20searching%20for%20predictive%20and%20preventive%20management%20solutions%2C%E2%80%9D%20recalls%20Vani%20in%20a%20conversation%20with%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHealth%20emergencies%2C%20like%20Bruno%E2%80%99s%2C%20made%20Vivek%20and%20Vani%20realise%20the%20need%20for%20devices%20that%20could%20monitor%20a%20pet%E2%80%99s%20vitals%20%E2%80%94%20similar%20to%20how%20humans%20track%20their%20blood%20pressure%2C%20oxygen%20levels%2C%20or%20blood%20sugar.%20When%20they%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20find%20reliable%20solutions%2C%20the%20Chennai-based%20duo%20decided%20to%20create%20their%20own.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%5Cn%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202018%2C%20they%20founded%20VETiNSTANT%2C%20an%20animal%20healthcare%20startup.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EBuilding%20an%20innovative%20platform%20for%20pet%20health%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20real%20work%20began%20in%202021%2C%20when%20they%20launched%20the%20venture%20as%20a%20bootstrapped%20initiative%20using%20their%20own%20resources.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%202021%2C%20we%20began%20designing%20an%20Apple-esque%20platform%20comprising%20a%20bed%2C%20bowl%2C%20and%20collar.%20The%20bed%20was%20intended%20to%20measure%20weight%20and%20sync%20the%20data%20to%20the%20cloud%2C%20the%20bowl%20to%20monitor%20food%20and%20water%20intake%2C%20and%20the%20collar%20to%20track%20vital%20signs%2C%E2%80%9D%20recalls%20Vani.%20%E2%80%9CHowever%2C%20when%20we%20presented%20the%20concept%20to%20veterinarians%2C%20they%20urged%20us%20to%20create%20a%20device%20capable%20of%20providing%20precise%20measurements%20and%20actionable%20data%20for%20accurate%20diagnosis%20and%20prognosis.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%5Cn%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20Vivek%20and%20Vani%20started%20the%20business%2C%20the%20first%20agency%20they%20hired%20was%20a%20Chennai-based%20law%20firm%20%E2%80%98KRIA%20Law%E2%80%99%20as%20they%20had%20patents%20to%20file%20on%20their%20inventions.%20They%20were%20recommended%20to%20the%20IIT%20Madras%20Incubation%20Cell%20by%20the%20founder%20of%20KRIA%20Law%2C%20M%20S%20Bharath.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAs%20we%20worked%20on%20the%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F263411%2Frashi-narang-heads-up-for-tails-delhi-pet-startup-earns-crores%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20bed%2C%20bowl%2C%20and%20collar%3C%2Fa%3E%20platform%20and%20began%20developing%20our%20proprietary%20device%2C%20we%20sought%20the%20expertise%20of%20KRIA%20Law%2C%20a%20legal%20agency%20that%20guided%20us%20in%20filing%20patents%20and%20a%20PCT%20(Patent%20Cooperation%20Treaty)%20for%20our%20IoT%20devices%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Vani.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETheir%20journey%20took%20a%20significant%20turn%20when%20Bharath%20introduced%20them%20to%20Professor%20Ashok%20Jhunjhunwala%2C%20who%20was%20thrilled%20by%20their%20innovative%20efforts.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20Incubation%20Cell%20has%20been%20instrumental%20in%20our%20growth%2C%20offering%20everything%20from%20office%20spaces%20to%20insightful%20mentoring%20sessions%20and%20valuable%20industry%20connections%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%20%E2%80%9CThey%E2%80%99ve%20supported%20us%20through%20funding%20discussions%2C%20pitch%20deck%20management%2C%20and%20more.%20They%20continue%20to%20be%20the%20wind%20beneath%20our%20wings.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%5Cn%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAssisting%20Vivek%20and%20Vani%20are%20chief%20technology%20officer%20Karthikeyan%20Gururaj%2C%20who%20also%20lost%20two%20of%20his%20pets%20to%20medical%20emergencies.%20For%20Karthikeyan%2C%20the%20startup%20was%20initially%20a%20client%20for%20technology%20platform%20development%20but%20he%20soon%20realised%20that%20the%20devices%20they%20were%20developing%20could%20have%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F268184%2Fdelhi-kitchen-for-paws-feed-stray-dogs-animals-food-divya-gurwara%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esaved%20his%20dogs%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20decided%20to%20join%20their%20mission.%20The%20fourth%20key%20person%20to%20join%20them%20was%20S%20Rajkumar%2C%20who%20is%20pursuing%20his%20master%E2%80%99s%20in%20biomedical%20design%20at%20IIT%20Madras.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EExam%20D%3A%20A%20non-invasive%20solution%20for%20accurate%20diagnoses%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBoth%20Vani%20and%20Vivek%20have%20three%20pet%20dogs%20each.%20As%20Vani%20argues%2C%20a%20major%20challenge%20in%20dealing%20with%20pet%20dogs%20is%20their%20high%20tolerance%20for%20pain%2C%20which%20makes%20it%20difficult%20for%20pet%20owners%20like%20her%20to%20recognise%20any%20real%20signs%20of%20discomfort.%20With%20a%20human%20child%2C%20you%20check%20their%20forehead%20to%20see%20if%20they%20have%20a%20fever%20and%20give%20them%20some%20soup.%20With%20dogs%2C%20however%2C%20you%20can%E2%80%99t%20touch%20their%20forehead%20and%20gauge%20whether%20they%20have%20a%20fever%20or%20not.%20Instead%2C%20you%20use%20devices%20like%20a%20rectal%20thermometer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVETiNSTANT%20replaced%20traditional%20rectal%20thermometers%20with%20a%20non-invasive%20device%20for%20diagnosing%20animal%20health.%20They%20also%20introduced%20a%20mobile%20app%2C%20making%20it%20easier%20for%20pet%20parents%20to%20connect%20with%20veterinarians%20for%20timely%20diagnosis%20and%20care.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%5Cn%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20500px)%20100vw%2C%20500px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2Fvet-device-1732274942-500x635.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Vetinstant's%20non-invasive%20device%20for%20Pet%20Parents%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2Fvet-device-1732274942-500x635.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2Fvet-device-1732274942-236x300.jpg%20236w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2Fvet-device-1732274942-150x190.jpg%20150w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2Fvet-device-1732274942.jpg%20541w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-382104%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22635%5C%22%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%E2%80%99s%20a%20handheld%2C%20IoT-driven%2C%20at%20home%20diagnostic%20device%2C%20that%20unlike%20its%20wearables%20counterparts%2C%20provides%20pet%20parents%20exact%20data%20with%20range%20information%20for%20temperature%2C%20heart%20rate%20or%20SpO2%20(oxygen%20saturation)%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Vivek.%20It%20took%20them%20about%20two%20years%20and%20four%20prototypes%20to%20arrive%20at%20their%20final%20product%20%E2%80%98Exam%20D%E2%80%99%2C%20which%20is%20%E2%80%9Cintegrated%20with%20our%20VETiNSTANT%20tracker%20app.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVani%20goes%20on%20to%20describe%20the%20motivation%20behind%20Exam%20D%3A%20%E2%80%9CThe%20need%20for%20a%20user-friendly%20consumer%20interface%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F380268%2Findiegood-sneha-baghrecha-sustainable-eco-friendly-pet-products-india-collaborations-animal-welfare-artisan-crafts-yoda-pfa%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eproduct%20for%20veterinarians%20and%20pet%20parents%3C%2Fa%3E%20inspired%20us%20to%20develop%20Exam%20D.%20This%20product%20is%20easy%20to%20use%20and%20features%20a%20graphical%20user%20interface%20that%20simplifies%20customer%20interaction.%20For%20the%20past%20two%20years%2C%20we%20have%20tested%20our%20prototypes%20in%20specific%20markets%20to%20validate%20usage%2C%20gather%20data%2C%20and%20gain%20acceptance%20from%20both%20veterinarians%20and%20pet%20parents.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHow%20to%20use%20Exam%20D%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnce%20the%20VETiNSTANT%20app%20is%20downloaded%20from%20the%20App%20Store%20or%20Play%20Store%2C%20users%20are%20asked%20to%20add%20their%20profile%20details%20followed%20by%20their%20pet%E2%80%99s%20details%20%E2%80%94%20whether%20they%20are%20one%20or%20many%20and%20what%20species%20they%20belong%20to.%20Users%20can%20buy%20the%20device%20from%20the%20startup%E2%80%99s%20website.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20two%20versions%20of%20Exam%20D.%20One%20measures%20temperature%20and%20performs%20heart%2C%20lung%20and%20abdomen%20auscultation%2C%20and%20is%20priced%20at%20Rs%206%2C500%20(inclusive%20of%20taxes).%20The%20other%20performs%20all%20the%20above%20but%20also%20gives%20pet%20owners%20readings%20for%20SpO2%20and%20heart%20rate%2C%20and%20costs%20Rs%209%2C000.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CYou%20only%20need%20to%20pair%20the%20app%20and%20device%20the%20first%20time%20when%20you%20buy%20the%20device.%20After%20that%2C%20all%20information%20presented%20in%20an%20executive%20summary%20will%20be%20available%20as%20a%20user%20goes%20through%20the%20prompts%20of%20the%20app%20and%20device%E2%80%99s%20graphic%20user%20interface%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20Vani.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EProfessor%20K%20Rajkumar%2C%20head%20of%20the%20Veterinary%20Clinical%20Complex%20at%20Rajiv%20Gandhi%20College%20of%20Veterinary%20and%20Animal%20Sciences%2C%20Pondicherry%2C%20explains%2C%20%E2%80%9CThis%20device%20is%20very%20convenient%2C%20especially%20for%20pet%20owners.%20They%20can%20easily%20use%20it%20to%20measure%20their%20pet%E2%80%99s%20temperature%2C%20heart%20rate%2C%20and%20lung%20(respiratory)%20sounds%20by%20simply%20placing%20it%20near%20the%20animal.%20The%20recorded%20data%20can%20then%20be%20shared%20with%20a%20veterinarian%20through%20telemedicine%20for%20further%20analysis.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20500px)%20100vw%2C%20500px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FSnapinsta.app_394118659_731097555730933_1985252946786160050_n_1080-1732274787-500x625.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Exam%20D%20device%20developed%20by%20Vetinstant%20for%20Pet%20Parents%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FSnapinsta.app_394118659_731097555730933_1985252946786160050_n_1080-1732274787-500x625.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FSnapinsta.app_394118659_731097555730933_1985252946786160050_n_1080-1732274787-240x300.jpg%20240w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FSnapinsta.app_394118659_731097555730933_1985252946786160050_n_1080-1732274787-150x188.jpg%20150w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FSnapinsta.app_394118659_731097555730933_1985252946786160050_n_1080-1732274787.jpg%20767w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-382095%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22625%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EIt%20took%20them%20about%20two%20years%20and%20four%20prototypes%20to%20arrive%20at%20their%20final%20product%20%E2%80%98Exam%20D%E2%80%99%2C%20which%20is%20%E2%80%9Cintegrated%20with%20our%20VETiNSTANT%20tracker%20app.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWith%20this%20device%2C%20we%20can%20accurately%20diagnose%20a%20pet%E2%80%99s%20condition%20using%20the%20recorded%20cardiac%20and%20lung%20sounds%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%20%E2%80%9CAnother%20key%20advantage%2C%20particularly%20for%20dogs%2C%20is%20that%20it%E2%80%99s%20non-invasive.%20Unlike%20rectal%20thermometers%2C%20which%20require%20regular%20sterilisation%2C%20Exam%20D%20offers%20a%20more%20comfortable%20alternative.%20Such%20devices%20are%20not%20yet%20available%20in%20India%2C%20so%20when%20the%20project%20proposal%20to%20standardise%20this%20equipment%20came%20to%20us%2C%20I%20was%20very%20excited.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20vets%2C%20the%20startup%20has%20introduced%20%E2%80%98Exam%20D%20Pro%E2%80%99%2C%20designed%20to%20help%20busy%20professionals%20on%20the%20go.%20It%20enables%20instant%20tracking%20of%20multiple%20vitals%20and%20provides%20quicker%20access%20to%20data%20during%20emergencies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20tracks%20multiple%20metrics%20that%20vets%20are%20trained%20to%20interpret%2C%20such%20as%20murmur%20identification%20and%20grading%20for%20early%20detection%20of%20heart%20conditions%2C%20lung%20abnormalities%2C%20and%20insights%20into%20issues%20like%20COPD%2C%20asthma%2C%20and%20wheezing%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20Vani.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20also%20provides%20trend%20analytics%2C%20continuous%20care%20insights%20for%20proactive%20health%20monitoring%2C%20and%20ECG%20readings%20to%20detect%20heart%20irregularities.%E2%80%9D%20Exam%20D%20Pro%20was%20launched%20alongside%20Exam%20D%20in%20early%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGoing%20further%2C%20they%20also%20brought%20on%20board%20medical%20professionals%20and%20developed%20a%20digitised%20system%20called%20PAWS%20(Pets%20Administration%20and%20Workflow%20System)%20for%20pet%20parents%20and%20veterinary%20clinics.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThrough%20this%20system%2C%20pet%20parents%20can%20directly%20connect%20with%20their%20vets.%20Vani%20said%20in%20a%20past%20interview%2C%20%E2%80%9CWith%20the%20device%2C%20there%20is%20an%20app%20that%20connects%20with%20the%20SaaS%20solution%20that%20the%20vet%20has.%20He%20has%20an%20app%20version%2C%20so%20he%20has%20data%20at%20his%20fingertips.%20All%20the%20data%20goes%20in%20a%20click%20of%20a%20button%20to%20the%20vet.%20They%20can%20set%20up%20calls%20online%20or%20offline.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FDCZF9okIh6V%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FDCZF9okIh6V%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3EView%20this%20post%20on%20Instagram%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv