%9CCommercial%20entities%20pay%20a%20premium%20tariff%20for%20power%20compared%20to%20domestic%20rates.%20While%20domestic%20rates%20average%20around%20Rs%205.5%20to%20Rs%206%20per%20unit%2C%20commercial%20tariffs%20can%20range%20from%20Rs%2015%20to%20Rs%2020%20in%20some%20areas.%20This%20makes%20model%20adoption%20faster%20since%20we%20can%20offer%20to%20install%20the%20panels%20on%20their%20rooftop%20and%20lower%20their%20power%20bills%20by%2030%20to%2040%25%20at%20no%20upfront%20cost%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20notes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFor%20them%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20immediate%20savings%20from%20day%20one%2C%20and%20they%20receive%20end-to-end%20solar%20power%20management%20without%20needing%20to%20worry%20about%20the%20project.%20One%20of%20the%20incentives%20for%20these%20entities%20to%20choose%20our%20model%20is%20that%20we%20operate%20the%20plant%20for%20the%20first%2015%20years%2C%20after%20which%20we%20hand%20it%20over%20to%20them%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%20376px)%20100vw%2C%20376px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FScreenshot-1732195815.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22376%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22With%20the%20way%2C%20SundayGrids%20is%20built%2C%20users%20can%20connect%20multiple%20utility%20accounts.%20(Image%20courtesy%20team-bhp)%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FScreenshot-1732195815.jpg%20376w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FScreenshot-1732195815-135x300.jpg%20135w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FScreenshot-1732195815-150x333.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-381858%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22835%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EWith%20the%20way%2C%20SundayGrids%20is%20built%2C%20users%20can%20connect%20multiple%20utility%20accounts.%20(Image%20courtesy%20team-bhp)%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAll%20the%20power%20generated%20by%20the%20plant%20gets%20dispatched%20into%20the%20building%E2%80%99s%20metre.%20This%20means%20the%20commercial%20entity%20avoids%20paying%20the%20grid%E2%80%99s%20premium%20rate%20and%20instead%20pays%20us%20a%20discounted%20rate%2C%20closer%20to%20domestic%20tariff%20levels%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20Naseer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COnce%20the%20plant%20is%20commissioned%2C%20we%20integrate%20it%20into%20our%20platform%2C%20making%20it%20available%20to%20all%20our%20users.%20Users%20can%20then%20reserve%20capacity%20based%20on%20their%20power%20bill%20offset%20goals.%20When%20the%20capacity%20assigned%20to%20a%20user%20generates%20power%2C%20the%20commercial%20entity%20pays%20us%20for%20that%20power%2C%20and%20we%20convert%20that%20payment%20into%20energy%20credits%20for%20the%20user.%20These%20energy%20credits%20are%20linked%20to%20the%20user%E2%80%99s%20utility%20accounts%20to%20offset%20their%20power%20bill%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHow%20does%20SundayGrids%20generate%20revenue%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20make%20a%20margin%20when%20users%20place%20a%20reservation.%20Solar%20developers%20also%20pay%20a%20recurring%20platform%20charge%20for%20listing%20and%20managing%20their%20projects.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20user%2C%20the%20advantages%20of%20buying%20into%20a%20SundayGrids%20project%20are%20clear.%20Going%20on%20social%20media%20and%20different%20online%20platforms%2C%20there%20are%20a%20variety%20of%20takes%20on%20the%20system%20they%20have%20built.%20While%20some%20are%20sceptical%20of%20the%20savings%2Freturns%20generated%20by%20buying%20into%20a%20commercial%20solar%20project%2C%20others%20see%20it%20as%20a%20means%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F305500%2Fpradeep-kumar-petwar-haryana-farmer-innovates-solar-on-wheel