ment%20Authority%20(OSDMA)%20to%20build%20a%20fire%20safety%20framework%20for%20the%20twin%20cities%20Bhubaneswar%20and%20Cuttack.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20team%20was%20happy%20when%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F370334%2Fsambit-kumar-das-founder-ek-asha-ngo-odisha-tribes-computers-english-maths-art-think-centers%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EOdisha%3C%2Fa%3E%20Government%20approached%20them%20for%20a%20blueprint.%20%E2%80%9CBeyond%20Carlton%20wants%20to%20be%20a%20force%20leading%20to%20positive%20change%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Venkitachalam%3B%20their%20credible%20work%20has%20pushed%20other%20states%20to%20adopt%20a%20similar%20model.%20Today%2C%20their%20blueprint%20facilitates%20all%20cities%20in%20Odisha.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSince%20Odisha%20has%20experience%20handling%20natural%20calamities%20with%20ease%2C%20they%20were%20more%20prepared%20and%20flexible%20for%20the%20suggested%20changes%2C%E2%80%9D%20Venkitachalam%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-gallery%20wp-block-gallery-1%20wp-block-gallery-is-layout-flex%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201080px)%20100vw%2C%201080px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2F279031372_5257968687558210_8385898760672421362_n_11zon-1731926307.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Workshop%20on%20comprehensive%20fire%20safety%20conducted%20in%20Bhubaneshwar%5C%22%20data-id%3D%5C%22380764%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2F279031372_5257968687558210_8385898760672421362_n_11zon-1731926307.jpg%201080w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2F279031372_5257968687558210_8385898760672421362_n_11zon-1731926307-300x300.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2F27