%20for%20the%20warriors%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUday%20points%20out%20the%20importance%20of%20understanding%20the%20emotional%20motive%20behind%20these%20awareness%20drives%20and%20blueprints.%20%E2%80%9COnce%20we%20lose%20the%20emotion%20of%20why%20we%20started%20this%20in%20the%20first%20place%2C%20our%20purpose%20fails%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEvery%20February%2C%20Beyond%20Carlton%20honours%20the%20nine%20lives%20lost%20in%20the%20tragedy%20by%20holding%20a%20memorial.%20The%20event%20includes%20conversations%20with%20changemakers%20and%20citizens%20working%20meticulously%20to%20prioritise%20fire%20safety%20and%20awareness.%20Musicians%20like%20Raghu%20Dixit%20also%20support%20the%20cause%20by%20showcasing%20their%20art%20form.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201024px)%20100vw%2C%201024px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FBC-memorial-2022-1731926121.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Members%20and%20citizens%20attend%20the%20Beyond%20Carlton%20Memorial%20in%202022%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FBC-memorial-2022-1731926121.jpg%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FBC-memorial-2022-1731926121-300x200.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FBC-memorial-2022-1731926121-500x333.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FBC-memorial-2022-1731926121-768x512.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FBC-memorial-2022-1731926121-150x100.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-380758%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22683%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EMembers%20and%20citizens%20attend%20the%20Beyond%20Carlton%20Memorial%20in%202022%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigur