%20face%20of%20%3Cem%3Emakhana%3C%2Fem%3E%20cultivation%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Manoj%20Kumar%20spent%20a%20decade%20researching%20ways%20to%20make%20%3Cem%3Emakhana%20%3C%2Fem%3Efarming%20more%20efficient%2C%20sustainable%2C%20and%20less%20labour-intensive.%20One%20of%20his%20breakthroughs%20was%20proving%20that%20%3Cem%3Emakhana%3C%2Fem%3E%20could%20thrive%20in%20water%20as%20shallow%20as%2030%20cm%2C%20contrary%20to%20the%20traditional%20belief%20that%20five%20to%20six%20feet%20was%20necessary.%20This%20discovery%20allowed%20farmers%20to%20grow%20%3Cem%3Emakhana%3C%2Fem%3E%20like%20any%20other%20crop%20in%20fields%2C%20reducing%20dependence%20on%20deep%2C%20flood-prone%20ponds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%5Cn%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Kumar%20also%20developed%20a%20high-yielding%20variety%20of%20%3Cem%3Emakhana%3C%2Fem%3E%20called%20%E2%80%98Swarna%20Vaidehi%3Cem%3E%E2%80%99%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%20a%20high-yielding%20variety%20of%20%3Cem%3Emakhana%3C%2Fem%3E.%20This%20variety%20adapted%20well%20to%20local%20conditions%20and%20significantly%20increased%20productivity.%20Additionally%2C%20techniques%20like%20nursery%20raising%20(growing%20seedlings%20separately%20before%20transplanting)%20and%20line%20planting%20(organised%20sowing%20in%20rows)%20were%20introduced.%20These%20methods%20reduced%20seed%20requirements%20and%20improved%20yields%2C%20making%20farming%20more%20efficient.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EOvercoming%20the%20flood%20challenge%20with%20innovative%20net%20fencing%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFloods%20have%20long%20been%20a%20major%20threat%20to%20%3Cem%3Emakhana%3C%2Fem%3E%20farming%2C%20often%20destroying%20entire%20crops.%20Dr%20Kumar%20tackled%20this%20issue%20by%20introducing%20net%20fencing%2C%20a%20simple%20yet%20effective%20solution.%20It%20involves%20installing%20mesh%20barriers%20around%20%3Cem%3Emakhana%20%3C%2Fem%3Efields%20to%20prot